channel.title: Working with somebody (forum maker)
channel.description:
Hey guys, basically if you have a server, but need a forums I am willing to work with you and make a forum for the server. I can also, if you don't want to work with me for some reason I'm willing to charge $5 to make a forums with pips added, crowns, topics(you want me to add) and other things you want me to do. But I prefer to be with somebody that has there own server up but just needs a forums. If you want me to make a forums or work with you and make a forums for the server pm me or post below.
I have no clue where to put this but I am going to post this under this topic because I see some people adv there server that don't have a forums, If so put this in the correct section. LIKE I SAID I KNOW THIS IS IN THE WRONG SECTION, BUT I COULDN'T FIND THE CORRECT SECTION TO POST THIS. Thank you.
